  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreWLAN\/CWKeychainDomain\ncrawled: 2026-03-10T14:35:07Z\n---\n\n# CWKeychainDomain\n\n**Enumeration**\n\nKeychain domain types that CoreWLAN keychain methods use.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\nenum CWKeychainDomain\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CWKeychainDomain.none**: No keychain domain specified.\n- **CWKeychainDomain.user**: The user keychain domain.\n- **CWKeychainDomain.system**: The system keychain domain.\n\n## Initializers\n\n- **init(rawValue:)**\n\n## Enumerations\n\n- **CWChannelBand**: CoreWLAN channel bands.\n- **CWChannelWidth**: CoreWLAN channel widths.\n- **CWCipherKeyFlags**: Cipher key flags.\n- **CWErr**\n- **CWEventType**: Wi-Fi event types.\n- **CWIBSSModeSecurity**: IBSS mode security types.\n- **CWInterfaceMode**: Wi-Fi interface operating modes.\n- **CWPHYMode**: CoreWLAN physical layer modes.\n- **CWSecurity**: CoreWLAN security types.\n\n## Conforms To\n\n- BitwiseCopyable\n- Equatable\n- Hashable\n- RawRepresentable\n- Sendable\n- SendableMetatype\n\n",
